{"tid":402110,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB Bigbig channel港姐做數，請專業點","createTime":"2017-09-16T07:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T00:16:57.000Z","uid":30647,"like":62,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ada16e5880e3ee4aff53f4b5f03b8f7ce36db83f","tid":402110,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TVB 做假請專業一點, 可以嗎？</span></span><br />\n<br />\nBigBig Channel 內各個佳麗的心心數字，由決賽前夕到昨天都被 ****** 覆蓋，無人知實際數字。<br />\n<br />\n終於今日BigBig Channel 內各個佳麗的心心數字重現。下面是 Screen Capture 做記錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/131458_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F131458_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=a7438187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面 Table 就列出各位佳麗在決賽前 (A), 決賽日 Battle 電視畫面顯示累計心心數目 (B), 以及現在 BBC 顯示的心心數目(C)。<br />\n<br />\n點解 (C) - (B) 會有負數?<br />\n點解依家心心數量仲少過 決賽當日 Battle 果陣畫面顯示嘅數目?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/131801_84c55a2df3db56a129cec098d9a22107.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F131801_84c55a2df3db56a129cec098d9a22107.jpg&h=51cb118a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf6d6565539db4840bdef45fbb0373bf36e0879e","tid":402110,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"DoDo姐一騎當千"},{"pid":"6088aa15dd313ae7c0d42f6deb2022d3727fb29a","tid":402110,"uid":20816,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:44:42.000Z","msg":"報ICAC或商業罪案調查科啦"},{"pid":"8e581d045a5a33389c83d291c2da76e811223fed","tid":402110,"uid":137470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:55:59.000Z","msg":"造假造到咁明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4777daea53